# Secure Cloud Storage

A simple cloud-based file storage system that encrypts files before uploading them, ensuring user privacy and data security.

## 🔒 Features
- Upload and encrypt files using AES encryption
- Store encrypted files securely on a cloud platform (e.g., AWS S3 or Firebase)
- Decrypt files for download by authorized users only

## 📌 Purpose
This project is part of my portfolio for the MEXT Undergraduate Scholarship 2026, showcasing my interest in cloud security.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Python + Flask
- Cryptography library (AES)
- Firebase / AWS S3
- HTML + CSS

## 🧠 Future Plans
- Add user login
- Two-factor authentication
- Access logs and alerts

